{"artefact":[["_response_info",{"status":"ok"}],["title","Getting an ASBO"],["id","https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/asbo.json"],["web_url","https://www.gov.uk/asbo"],["format","answer"],["details",{"need_id":"473","business_proposition":false,"alternative_title":"Getting an Anti-social Behaviour Order (ASBO)","overview":"Find out what happens if you are given an Anti-social Behaviour Order (ASBO).","updated_at":"2012-10-02T12:13:04+00:00","body":"\n<div class=\"summary\">\n<p>Anyone over the age of 10 can get an Anti-social Behaviour Order (<abbr title=\"Anti-social Behaviour Order\">ASBO</abbr>)</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>You can get an <abbr title=\"Anti-social Behaviour Order\">ASBO</abbr> if you have behaved &lsquo;anti-socially&rsquo;. This includes:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>drunken or threatening behaviour</li>\n  <li>vandalism and graffiti</li>\n  <li>playing loud music at night</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Getting an <abbr title=\"Anti-social Behaviour Order\">ASBO</abbr> means you won&rsquo;t be allowed to do certain things, such as:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>going to a particular place, eg your local town centre</li>\n  <li>spending time with people who are known as trouble-makers</li>\n  <li>drinking in the street</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>If you get an <abbr title=\"Anti-social Behaviour Order\">ASBO</abbr> it will last for at least 2 years. It could be reviewed if your behaviour improves.</p>\n\n<p>If you don\u2019t obey the <abbr title=\"Anti-social Behaviour Order\">ASBO</abbr>, you could be taken to court.</p>\n\n"}],["tags",[{"title":"Courts, sentencing and tribunals","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/tags/justice%2Fcourts-sentencing-tribunals.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Attending courts, paying fines, appealing a sentence and tribunals","type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/with_tag.json?tag=justice%2Fcourts-sentencing-tribunals","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/justice/courts-sentencing-tribunals"},"parent":{"title":"Crime, justice and the law","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/tags/justice.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Legal processes, courts and the police","type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/with_tag.json?tag=justice","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/justice"},"parent":null}}]],["related",[{"title":"Report a crime or anti-social behaviour","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/report-crime-anti-social-behaviour.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/report-crime-anti-social-behaviour","format":"answer","details":{"need_id":"279","business_proposition":false}},{"title":"Resolving neighbour disputes","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/how-to-resolve-neighbour-disputes.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/how-to-resolve-neighbour-disputes","format":"guide","details":{"need_id":"214","business_proposition":false}},{"title":"Report vandalism","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/report-vandalism.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/report-vandalism","format":"local_transaction","details":{"need_id":"2159","business_proposition":false}}]]],"parts":null}